
NOTES
=====

* human-readable format for automata (->src/automata.cpp::read_automaton()/write_automaton())
	[general]
	is dfa=true;
	alphabet size=4;
	number of states=5;
	[initial states]
	1,2,3, ...;
	[final states]
	...;
	[transitions]
	q,l,q;
	...;




